    "body": "A little hack that I came up with, which can be used as an alternative until this is fixed. But this too probably has its own set of problems. \r\n\r\n\r\n`[custom.fossil_hack]`\r\n`disabled = false`\r\n`command = 'fossil diff -i --numstat | awk \"END{if (\\$1 || \\$2) printf \\\"\\033[32m+%d \\033[31m-%d\\033[0m\\\", \\$1, \\$2}\"'`\r\n`when = 'fossil status'` \r\n`shell = ['/usr/bin/bash']`\r\n`format = '[$output](fg:color_aqua bg:color_blue)($style)'`\r\n",
